<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pestilence" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pestilence,</orth> plague, contagious disease: <bibl n="shak. ven 740" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 740</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.87" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 1, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.284" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 284</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.3.87" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 1, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.2.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 2, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.362" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 362</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.10.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 10, 9</bibl>. <cit><quote>to have the p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 1, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a p. on him!</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 2, 21</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 196</bibl>. <cit><quote>the red p. strike all trades in Rome,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.1.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 1, 13</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the most infectious p. upon thee!</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.5.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 5, 61</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>